headline: Textron Aviation Defense Launches Nationwide Tour Showcasing Beechcraft M-346N Capabilities for U.S. Navy
summary: WICHITA, Kan., September 16, 2025--The Beechcraft M-346N set off on a nationwide tour as a ready-now total solution for the U.S. Navy Undergraduate Jet Training System program.
